Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:54.84,OP2-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}若能变得更强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.55,OP2-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,	{\blur1\fad(100,100)}眼前的这个天空
